beverly hills chihuahua is a 2012 american family comedy film directed by alex zamm , and starring george lopez , odette annable and zachary gordon . it is the sequel to the family comedy film beverly hills chihuahua 3 : viva la fiesta ! : viva la fiesta ! : viva la fiesta ! : viva la fiesta ! : viva la fiesta ! : viva la fiesta ! , was released on september 18 , 2012 .